    <node id="马云">
      <data key="entity_id">马云</data>
      <data key="entity_type">person</data>
      <data key="description">马云is a prominent figure who was born in浙江省嵊州市, later relocated to杭州, and has a significant background in education and English teaching which laid a foundation for his future career.&lt;SEP&gt;马云is a notable figure who graduated from杭州师范学院, receiving a bachelor's degree in English and later engaged in English teaching.</data>
